r1889 | caseydk | 2011-05-07 00:00:13 -0500 (Sat, 07 May 2011) | 1 line
Changed paths:
   M /trunk/install/sql/mysql/019_add_system_timezone.sql
   D /trunk/install/sql/mysql/034_setup_timezones.sql

This was merged from Robert Basic's timezone patch included in https://github.com/caseysoftware/web2project/pull/24 It was shifted from being an independent sql statement - 034_setup_timezones.sql - to being applied immediately after the timezones are added. This will prevent existing systems from being corrupted.
