r1617 | pedroix | 2011-02-10 11:16:35 -0600 (Thu, 10 Feb 2011) | 6 lines
Changed paths:
   M /trunk/includes/main_functions.php

1) Did anyone ever wondered why at some point the icons started to behave not in an inline manner?
For example the icons on he contacts module list were stacked instead of being side by side.
Or on the System Config, the tips icons were below the configuration boxes.
Well this fixes it.

