r1519 | caseydk | 2010-12-07 01:36:11 -0600 (Tue, 07 Dec 2010) | 5 lines
Changed paths:
   M /trunk/modules/tasks/do_task_aed.php
   M /trunk/modules/tasks/tasks.class.php

eliminated the option of a child task being dependent on the parent task;
inherently as a child task, it is part of the parent and therefore shouldn't be dependent on the parent being complete;
more importantly, this was causing a task circular reference which began a paradox that The Doctor had to fix, the 10th Doctor to be specific;

resolves http://bugs.web2project.net/view.php?id=556
------------------------------------------------------------------------
r1518 | caseydk | 2010-12-07 01:09:52 -0600 (Tue, 07 Dec 2010) | 3 lines
